      "line": 31,
      "message": "In theory yes.\nCurrently when we run command \"mvn clean install\", only SNAPSHOT tags are generated.\nFor example, in this case guilin branch:\n\n1.0.3-SNAPSHOT\n1.0.3-SNAPSHOT-latest\n1.0.3-SNAPSHOT-null\n\nThese three tags are generated.\nWe need to do a little extra work to tag non-snapshot.",
